# Benchmark baselines (ordo-one/benchmark) are machine-specific scratch. Only a runner-generated
# `main` baseline is ever committed — and it is force-added (`git add -f`) from CI — so the
# directory is ignored wholesale to keep local-machine numbers out of the repo.
/.benchmarkBaselines/

